BT Real Estat Requirements

--FRONTENT--
- Home	
- About
- Listings
- Single Listings
- Search
- Register
- Login
- Dashboard (inquiries)


--DESIGN SPECS--
- Use BTRE Logo (Frontend & Admin)
- Brand colors (blue #10284c / green #30caa0)
- Mobile Friendly
- Social Media icons & contact info
- Clean design


--FUNCTIONALITY--
- Manage listings, realtors, contact inquiries and website users via admin
- Role based user (staff and non-staff)
- Display listings in app with pagination
- Ability to set listings to unpublished
- Search listing by keyword, city, state, bedrooms and prive (Homepage & search page)
- List realtors on about page with 'Seller of the month' (control via admin)
- Listing page should have fields listed below*
- listing page should have 5-6 img with lighbox
- Lightbox should scroll through images
- Listintgs page should have a form to submit inquirey for property listing
- Form info should go to database and notify realtors with an email
- Frontend register/login to track inquiries
- Both registered and unregistered users can submit form. If user is registered, can only submit one / listing


*--LISTING PAGE FIELDS--

- Title
- Address, city, state, zip
- Price
- Bedrooms
- Bathrooms
- Square Feet
- Lot Size
- Garage
- Listing date
- Realtor (Name & Img)
- Main image + 5 other images




